worldgen.title: Tectonic
worldgen.desc: A beautiful datapack featuring 20+ custom biomes, magnificent mountain ranges, and long underground rivers.

worldgen.title: William Wythers' Overhauled Overworld
worldgen.desc: With over 200 new biomes, this pack focuses on making Minecraft both realistic and beautiful.

worldgen.title: FokaStudio's Ender Expansion
worldgen.desc: This end overhaul has not only 15+ biomes, but new terrain, structures, weapons, and mobs as well.

worldgen.title: Luminous End
worldgen.desc: If you have a wild imagination, this datapack's fantastical terrain, biomes, and mobs are for you!

worldgen.title: Cavernous
worldgen.desc: This pack is great for miners; adding new vanilla-like cave biomes, as well as a couple items, advancements, and structures.

worldgen.title: Overgrown Overworld
worldgen.desc: Noticing Vanilla's lack of proper foliage, this pack adds towering trees, giant foliage, and heaps of life.

worldgen.title: The Swift Biomes
worldgen.desc: Calling all Swifties: you can explore 9 well-crafted biomes, reimagining the beauty of each of Taylor's 9 studio albums.

resourcepack.title: Biome Colored Lava
resourcepack.desc: A simple pack designed to make lava change color based on the biome its in - compatible with several nether packs.

resourcepack.title: Terralith Addon Sakura
resourcepack.desc: This is one of serveral add-on packs for Terralith to improve the look and atmosphere of certain biomes.

resourcepack.title: Better Botanicals: Vegetation
resourcepack.desc: One of Botany's most popular packs, textures and models of saplings, leaves, sticks, and other vegetation is reimagined.

datapack.title: Florcraft
datapack.desc: Inspired by Thaumcraft, this magic datapack uses essence you collect to create powerful staves and tools.

datapack.title: ULTRIS
datapack.desc: For all the boss lovers out there, 8 unique bosses can be found with their own quests and rewards.

datapack.title: New in Town
datapack.desc: Thrown into a story, you are tasked with defending your own settlement from the forces from the Nether.

datapack.title: Dungeon Now Loading
datapack.desc: This datapack combines 10+ vanilla=like structures with custom bosses, advancements, items, and custom health system.

datapack.title: Terralith Biome Sapling Compatibility
datapack.desc: A simple Terralith add-on made to have saplings grow into their respective custom tree, based on the biome planted in.

datapack.title: RPG Classes
datapack.desc: An artfully made RPG classes datapack that is fun and unique, while not being destructive and op like many other packs out there.

datapack.title: Vanilla Refresh
datapack.desc: Focused on QOL, this pack has features such as sitting, void totems, xp from crops, Minecraft tips, and much more.

datapack.title: BlazeandCave's Advancements
datapack.desc: One of the first advancement packs created, this pack adds 900+ advancements, and pairs nicely with Stardust Labs' packs.

structure.title: Repurposed Structures
structure.desc: This mod is dedicated to taking existing vanilla structures, improving them, and creating variants in a vanilla-friendly way.

structure.title: Immersive Structures
structure.desc: Structures in this pack are uniquely designed to bring immersion and atmosphere with a variety of different builds.

structure.title: Towns & Towers
structure.desc: Expanding on the Village and Pillage update, this pack adds new villages, pillager outposts, and even ships to liven up the world.

structure.title: ChoiceTheorem's Overhauled Villages
structure.desc: True to its name, this pack adds 20+ brand new and breathtaking village and pillager outposts, built from the ground up.

structure.title: Hopo Better Mineshafts
structure.desc: Minecraft's mineshafts are lackluster - this datapack adds 9+ new Mineshafts, complete with unique rooms and loot.

structure.title: YUNG's Better Desert Temples
structure.desc: One of several YUNG's mods, this one completely revamps vanilla desert temples with exciting puzzles, traps, parkour, and loot.
